descriptionHtml:
MOD IS IN SPANISH!


common snakes

based on exellent mihail giant snakes

this snakes are from level 1 to 20 (levels w/player)
very weak attack
very low hp (like skeever or wolf)
weak poison but with long duration (5 minutes)


they are placed on immersive locations, forests, marshs, and caves.



credits to mihail for the 99% of the work(i've only adapted his snakes to my version)
